HandleLinkDesc:
If enabled, the download link will be handled by the downloader.
You can hold the Ctrl and click the link to skip handle the link.
HandleLinkDomainDesc: If you are in private server, you should change this, otherwise, keep it default.
GrantOsuAccountDesc:
Grant osu! account, then you can download beatmaps by officially, just like osu!direct.
NOTICE: If you are in private server, please don not enable this.
NotGrantOsuAccountButUseOfficialWarn:
WARNING: You are NOT grant osu! account but using official download!
The all of download tasks will AUTO CANCELLED!
ProxyServerDesc: Use proxy server to search/download beatmaps.
CustomUserAgentDesc: Enable Custom User-Agent, If you don't know what it is, please keep it disabled.
Title: Title: %s
HotkeyDesc:
[%s] Toggle MainUi Show.
[%s] Toggle BeatmapIdSearchUi Show.
Hold [Ctrl] + Click the link to skip handle the link.
Hold [SHIFT] + Click the link to direct download the beatmap(except exists beatmap).
SearchBeatmapIdDesc:
Search beatmap by id.By BeatmapSetsId: beatmapsets123456 | s123456。
By BeatmapId: beatmaps123456 | b123456
Only number id: by left combo box selected.
DownloadFailedOORT: Download beatmapsets(%d) failed! (out of retry times)
OsuPathDesc:
Use custom osu! path, or empty to auto detect the path.
If you don't know what it is, please keep it empty.
MoveToOsuFolderDesc: Move downloaded beatmap to osu! Songs folder instead open the .osz file.
MultiDownloaderDesc:
Download multiple beatmaps line by line.
e.g.:
s123456
123456
https://osu.ppy.sh/beatmapsets/123456
